&mt_exit_AML_on_tap LCTRL ESCAPE  &kp LEFT_WIN         &kp AT                            &lt 3 TAB  &lt 4 SPACE  &kp BACKSPACE     &lt 4 ENTER                     &kp trans       &lt 6 LC(SPACE)      &kp END
&kp LEFT   &kp UP     &kp SPACE  &kp DOWN   &kp RIGHT                            &kp HOME   &kp PG_UP  &kp ENTER  &kp PG_DN  &kp END
                                 &kp A                                                      &kp B
            >;

