&mt_exit_AML_on_tap LEFT_CONTROL SINGLE_QUOTE  &kp LEFT_SHIFT                                 &kp LEFT_CONTROL            &to 0              &mo 1           &kp DELETE  &kp K_APP                                           &kp trans    &mo 6 &kp trans 
&kp LEFT      &kp UP    &kp SPACE  &kp DOWN  &kp RIGHT                                          &kp HOME       &kp PG_UP  &kp ENTER  &kp PG_DN  &kp END
